51 int __TBB_load_ittnotify() {
52 #if !(_WIN32||_WIN64)
53  // tool_api crashes without dlopen, check that it's present. Common case
54  // for lack of dlopen is static binaries, i.e. ones build with -static.
55  if (dlopen == NULL)
56  return 0;
57 #endif
58  return __itt_init_ittlib(NULL, // groups for:

64 }
